CHECK:COMPARISON_TO_NULL: Comparison to NULL could be written "!fl"
#68: FILE: fs/locks.c:1394:
+	if (fl == NULL)

Comparisons to NULL in the form (foo == NULL) or (foo != NULL)
are better written as (!foo) and (foo).

